#include<bits/stdc++.h>

using namespace std;

const int leap[] = {0,31,60,91,121,152,182,213,244,274,305,335,366};
const int nonleap[] = {0,31,59,90,120,151,181,212,243,273,304,334,365};

int main(){
    map<const string,int> m;
    m.insert(make_pair("JAN",1));
    m.insert(make_pair("FEB",2));
    m.insert(make_pair("MAR",3));
    m.insert(make_pair("APR",4));
    m.insert(make_pair("MAY",5));
    m.insert(make_pair("JUN",6));
    m.insert(make_pair("JUL",7));
    m.insert(make_pair("AUG",8));
    m.insert(make_pair("SEP",9));
    m.insert(make_pair("OCT",10));
    m.insert(make_pair("NOV",11));
    m.insert(make_pair("DEC",12));
    int t;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    for(int i = 1; i <= t; ++i){
        int d,y;
        char month[4];
        scanf("%2d-%3s-%4d",&d,month,&y);
        const int *thisyear = nonleap;
        if(y % 400 == 0 or (y % 100 != 0 and y % 4 == 0))
            thisyear = leap;
        int days = d + thisyear[m[string(month)]-1];
        if(days > 360)
            printf("Case %d: %d Ones\n",i,days - 360);
        else if(days > 300)
            printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",i,days - 300);
        else
            printf("Case %d: %d Hundreds\n",i,days);
    }
}
